# NexTalk

A modern real-time communication platform built with React, Express, Socket.IO, Prisma, and PostgreSQL.

## 🚀 Live Demo

Frontend: https://nextalk-1-nvjl.onrender.com

Backend API: https://nextalk-39xw.onrender.com

## Features

- Real-time messaging with Socket.IO
- JWT Authentication
- Private one-to-one conversations
- Responsive modern UI
- PostgreSQL + Prisma ORM
- Cloud deployment on Render
